Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.publishing.common.ncf.messages

messages used by the native communication framework (NCF).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IProcessableMessage Interface defining methods needed that the server can process an incoming method.
 

Class Summary
AbstractMessageBase Abstract base class for messages between client and server in NCF.
AbstractServiceMessage Abstract base class for service messages between server and client.
AbstractServiceMethodMessage Abstract base class for service method messages between client and server.
AbstractServiceNotification Base class for notifications.
AbstractServicePublishedMessage A service published message from the server to the client.
ExceptionResponseMessage Message for exceptions that occur on the server.
GetFileDetailsCommand Message that can be sent to the server to get the details (size, last modification date) of a file.
GetFileDetailsResponseMessage Response message that is sent to the client after requesting detailed information of a file from the server's file system.
KeepAliveMessage Message that is used to keep the connection alive while it is idle detecting lost connections also.
ServiceAvailabilityCheckCommand A service availability check message from the client to the server.
ServiceAvailabilityCheckResponse A service availability check response message from the server to the client.
ServiceClientRequest Request message from the server to the client.
ServiceClientResponseMessage Message for returning a response from the client to the server due to a server request.
ServiceMethodCallCommand A method call request message from the client to the server.
ServiceMethodCallResponse A method call response message from the server to the client.
ServiceMethodExceptionNotification Exception notification that is sent, when method that is subscribed throws an exception.
ServiceMethodNotification Notification message for changes in method return values.
ServiceMethodSubscribeCommand Message for starting subscription on method result changes.
ServiceNotification Notification message from the server.
ServicePublishedMessage A service published message from the server to the client.
ServiceSubscribeCommand Message for subscribing for changes on service.
ServiceSubscribeResponse response message for ServiceMethodSubscribeCommands.
SessionHandshakeMessage Message that is used for the handshake between the client and the server session.
StartFileTransferAsyncCommand Message for signaling the server that a file transfer from to a client can be started.
